name: Crowbar Climber
summary:
🚀 The Space Odyssey Update is Here! 🚀
Defy gravity in the new stage: Comic Ascent! Experience half-gravity climbing and use powerful dash devices to blast through the stars. Team up with friends and conquer the void together! Just don’t get lost in orbit!

This game is a challenge for all VR gamers who love physics and brain teasers.
For VR gamers who are strong in both mind and arm... see you at the top!
